%% E068 - Search flow sequence - F1-6 API Rulings
%% Source: docs/design/f1-6-api-rulings.md (E067), specs 4.2
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Controller as RulingsController
    participant MediatR
    participant Validation as ValidationBehavior
    participant Handler as SearchRulingsHandler
    participant Embedding as IEmbeddingService
    participant Search as ISearchService
    participant Mapper as AutoMapper

    Client->>Controller: POST /api/rulings/search (body)
    Controller->>MediatR: Send(SearchRulingsQuery)
    MediatR->>Validation: Validate
    Validation-->>MediatR: ok
    MediatR->>Handler: Handle(SearchRulingsQuery)
    Handler->>Embedding: GenerateAsync(query)
    Embedding-->>Handler: embedding vector
    Handler->>Search: SearchAsync(embedding, filters, page, pageSize)
    Search-->>Handler: raw results
    Handler->>Mapper: Map to SearchRulingsResult
    Mapper-->>Handler: SearchRulingsResult
    Handler-->>MediatR: SearchRulingsResult
    MediatR-->>Controller: SearchRulingsResult
    Controller->>Client: 200 OK (JSON)
